{"segment_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0001", "section_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i", "source_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 1, "text_original": "子墨子言曰：", "text_normalized": "子墨子言曰：", "canonical_ref": "27.1", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0002", "section_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i", "source_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 2, "text_original": "古者王公大人為政國家者，皆欲國家之富，人民之眾，刑政之治。", "text_normalized": "古者王公大人為政國家者，皆欲國家之富，人民之眾，刑政之治。", "canonical_ref": "27.2", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0003", "section_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i", "source_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 3, "text_original": "然而不得富而得貧，不得眾而得寡，不得治而得亂，則是本失其所欲，得其所惡，是故何也？", "text_normalized": "然而不得富而得貧，不得眾而得寡，不得治而得亂，則是本失其所欲，得其所惡，是故何也？", "canonical_ref": "27.3", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0004", "section_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i", "source_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 4, "text_original": "子墨子言曰：", "text_normalized": "子墨子言曰：", "canonical_ref": "27.4", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0005", "section_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i", "source_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 5, "text_original": "執有命者以雜於民間者眾。", "text_normalized": "執有命者以雜於民間者眾。", "canonical_ref": "27.5", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0006", "section_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i", "source_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 6, "text_original": "執有命者之言曰：", "text_normalized": "執有命者之言曰：", "canonical_ref": "27.6", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0007", "section_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i", "source_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 7, "text_original": "「命富則富，命貧則貧，命眾則眾，命寡則寡，命治則治，命亂則亂，命壽則壽，命夭則夭。", "text_normalized": "「命富則富，命貧則貧，命眾則眾，命寡則寡，命治則治，命亂則亂，命壽則壽，命夭則夭。", "canonical_ref": "27.7", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0008", "section_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i", "source_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 8, "text_original": "命雖強勁，何益哉？", "text_normalized": "命雖強勁，何益哉？", "canonical_ref": "27.8", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0009", "section_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i", "source_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 9, "text_original": "」上以說王公大人，下以駔百姓之從事。", "text_normalized": "」上以說王公大人，下以駔百姓之從事。", "canonical_ref": "27.9", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0010", "section_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i", "source_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 10, "text_original": "故執有命者不仁，故當執有命者之言，不可不明辨。", "text_normalized": "故執有命者不仁，故當執有命者之言，不可不明辨。", "canonical_ref": "27.10", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0011", "section_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i", "source_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 11, "text_original": "然則明辨此之說，將奈何哉？", "text_normalized": "然則明辨此之說，將奈何哉？", "canonical_ref": "27.11", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0012", "section_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i", "source_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 12, "text_original": "子墨子言曰：", "text_normalized": "子墨子言曰：", "canonical_ref": "27.12", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0013", "section_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i", "source_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 13, "text_original": "言必立儀。", "text_normalized": "言必立儀。", "canonical_ref": "27.13", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0014", "section_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i", "source_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 14, "text_original": "言而毋儀，譬猶運鈞之上而立朝夕者也，是非利害之辨，不可得而明知也。", "text_normalized": "言而毋儀，譬猶運鈞之上而立朝夕者也，是非利害之辨，不可得而明知也。", "canonical_ref": "27.14", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0015", "section_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i", "source_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 15, "text_original": "故言必有三表。", "text_normalized": "故言必有三表。", "canonical_ref": "27.15", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0016", "section_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i", "source_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 16, "text_original": "何謂三表？", "text_normalized": "何謂三表？", "canonical_ref": "27.16", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0017", "section_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i", "source_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 17, "text_original": "子墨子言曰：", "text_normalized": "子墨子言曰：", "canonical_ref": "27.17", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0018", "section_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i", "source_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 18, "text_original": "有本之者，有原之者，有用之者。", "text_normalized": "有本之者，有原之者，有用之者。", "canonical_ref": "27.18", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0019", "section_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i", "source_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 19, "text_original": "於何本之？", "text_normalized": "於何本之？", "canonical_ref": "27.19", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0020", "section_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i", "source_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 20, "text_original": "上本之於古者聖王之事。", "text_normalized": "上本之於古者聖王之事。", "canonical_ref": "27.20", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0021", "section_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i", "source_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 21, "text_original": "於何原之？", "text_normalized": "於何原之？", "canonical_ref": "27.21", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0022", "section_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i", "source_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 22, "text_original": "下原察百姓耳目之實。", "text_normalized": "下原察百姓耳目之實。", "canonical_ref": "27.22", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0023", "section_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i", "source_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 23, "text_original": "於何用之？", "text_normalized": "於何用之？", "canonical_ref": "27.23", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0024", "section_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i", "source_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 24, "text_original": "廢以為刑政，觀其中國家百姓人民之利。", "text_normalized": "廢以為刑政，觀其中國家百姓人民之利。", "canonical_ref": "27.24", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0025", "section_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i", "source_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 25, "text_original": "此所謂言有三表也。", "text_normalized": "此所謂言有三表也。", "canonical_ref": "27.25", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0026", "section_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i", "source_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 26, "text_original": "然而今天下之士君子，或以命為有，蓋嘗尚觀於聖王之事。", "text_normalized": "然而今天下之士君子，或以命為有，蓋嘗尚觀於聖王之事。", "canonical_ref": "27.26", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0027", "section_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i", "source_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 27, "text_original": "古者桀之所亂，湯受而治之。", "text_normalized": "古者桀之所亂，湯受而治之。", "canonical_ref": "27.27", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0028", "section_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i", "source_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 28, "text_original": "紂之所亂，武王受而治之。", "text_normalized": "紂之所亂，武王受而治之。", "canonical_ref": "27.28", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0029", "section_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i", "source_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 29, "text_original": "此世未易，民未渝，在於桀、紂則天下亂，在於湯、武則天下治。", "text_normalized": "此世未易，民未渝，在於桀、紂則天下亂，在於湯、武則天下治。", "canonical_ref": "27.29", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0030", "section_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i", "source_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 30, "text_original": "豈可謂有命哉！", "text_normalized": "豈可謂有命哉！", "canonical_ref": "27.30", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0031", "section_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i", "source_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 31, "text_original": "然而今天下之士君子，或以命為有，蓋嘗尚觀於先王之書。", "text_normalized": "然而今天下之士君子，或以命為有，蓋嘗尚觀於先王之書。", "canonical_ref": "27.31", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0032", "section_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i", "source_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 32, "text_original": "先王之書，所以出國家、佈施百姓者，憲也。", "text_normalized": "先王之書，所以出國家、佈施百姓者，憲也。", "canonical_ref": "27.32", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0033", "section_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i", "source_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 33, "text_original": "先王之憲亦嘗有曰「福不可請，而禍不可諱，敬無益、暴無傷」者乎？", "text_normalized": "先王之憲亦嘗有曰「福不可請，而禍不可諱，敬無益、暴無傷」者乎？", "canonical_ref": "27.33", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0034", "section_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i", "source_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 34, "text_original": "所以聽獄制罪者，刑也。", "text_normalized": "所以聽獄制罪者，刑也。", "canonical_ref": "27.34", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0035", "section_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i", "source_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 35, "text_original": "先王之刑亦嘗有曰「福不可請，禍不可諱，敬無益、暴無傷」者乎？", "text_normalized": "先王之刑亦嘗有曰「福不可請，禍不可諱，敬無益、暴無傷」者乎？", "canonical_ref": "27.35", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0036", "section_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i", "source_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 36, "text_original": "所以整設師旅、進退師徒者，誓也。", "text_normalized": "所以整設師旅、進退師徒者，誓也。", "canonical_ref": "27.36", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0037", "section_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i", "source_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 37, "text_original": "先王之誓亦嘗有曰「福不可請，禍不可諱，敬無益、暴無傷」者乎？", "text_normalized": "先王之誓亦嘗有曰「福不可請，禍不可諱，敬無益、暴無傷」者乎？", "canonical_ref": "27.37", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0038", "section_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i", "source_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 38, "text_original": "是故子墨子言曰：", "text_normalized": "是故子墨子言曰：", "canonical_ref": "27.38", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0039", "section_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i", "source_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 39, "text_original": "吾當未鹽數，天下之良書不可盡計數，大方論數，而五者是也。", "text_normalized": "吾當未鹽數，天下之良書不可盡計數，大方論數，而五者是也。", "canonical_ref": "27.39", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0040", "section_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i", "source_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 40, "text_original": "今雖毋求執有命者之言，不必得，不亦可錯乎。", "text_normalized": "今雖毋求執有命者之言，不必得，不亦可錯乎。", "canonical_ref": "27.40", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0041", "section_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i", "source_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 41, "text_original": "今用執有命者之言，是覆天下之義。", "text_normalized": "今用執有命者之言，是覆天下之義。", "canonical_ref": "27.41", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0042", "section_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i", "source_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 42, "text_original": "覆天下之義者，是立命者也，百姓之誶也。", "text_normalized": "覆天下之義者，是立命者也，百姓之誶也。", "canonical_ref": "27.42", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0043", "section_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i", "source_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 43, "text_original": "說百姓之誶者，是滅天下之人也。", "text_normalized": "說百姓之誶者，是滅天下之人也。", "canonical_ref": "27.43", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0044", "section_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i", "source_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 44, "text_original": "然則所為欲義在上者，何也？", "text_normalized": "然則所為欲義在上者，何也？", "canonical_ref": "27.44", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0045", "section_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i", "source_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 45, "text_original": "曰：", "text_normalized": "曰：", "canonical_ref": "27.45", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0046", "section_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i", "source_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 46, "text_original": "義人在上，天下必治，上帝、山川、鬼神必有干主，萬民被其大利。", "text_normalized": "義人在上，天下必治，上帝、山川、鬼神必有干主，萬民被其大利。", "canonical_ref": "27.46", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0047", "section_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i", "source_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 47, "text_original": "何以知之？", "text_normalized": "何以知之？", "canonical_ref": "27.47", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0048", "section_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i", "source_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 48, "text_original": "子墨子曰：", "text_normalized": "子墨子曰：", "canonical_ref": "27.48", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0049", "section_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i", "source_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 49, "text_original": "古者湯封於亳，絕長繼短，方地百里，與其百姓兼相愛，交相利，移則分。", "text_normalized": "古者湯封於亳，絕長繼短，方地百里，與其百姓兼相愛，交相利，移則分。", "canonical_ref": "27.49", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0050", "section_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i", "source_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 50, "text_original": "率其百姓，以上尊天事鬼。", "text_normalized": "率其百姓，以上尊天事鬼。", "canonical_ref": "27.50", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0051", "section_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i", "source_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 51, "text_original": "是以天鬼富之，諸侯與之，百姓親之，賢士歸之，未歿其世而王天下，政諸侯。", "text_normalized": "是以天鬼富之，諸侯與之，百姓親之，賢士歸之，未歿其世而王天下，政諸侯。", "canonical_ref": "27.51", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0052", "section_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i", "source_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 52, "text_original": "昔者文王封於岐周，絕長繼短，方地百里，與其百姓兼相愛，交相利，則，是以近者安其政，遠者歸其德。", "text_normalized": "昔者文王封於岐周，絕長繼短，方地百里，與其百姓兼相愛，交相利，則，是以近者安其政，遠者歸其德。", "canonical_ref": "27.52", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0053", "section_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i", "source_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 53, "text_original": "聞文王者皆起而趨之，罷不肖股肱不利者，處而願之，曰：", "text_normalized": "聞文王者皆起而趨之，罷不肖股肱不利者，處而願之，曰：", "canonical_ref": "27.53", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0054", "section_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i", "source_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 54, "text_original": "「奈何乎使文王之地及我吾，則吾利豈不亦猶文王之民也哉！", "text_normalized": "「奈何乎使文王之地及我吾，則吾利豈不亦猶文王之民也哉！", "canonical_ref": "27.54", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0055", "section_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i", "source_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 55, "text_original": "」是以天鬼富之，諸侯與之，百姓親之，賢士歸之。", "text_normalized": "」是以天鬼富之，諸侯與之，百姓親之，賢士歸之。", "canonical_ref": "27.55", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0056", "section_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i", "source_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 56, "text_original": "未歿其世而王天下，政諸侯。", "text_normalized": "未歿其世而王天下，政諸侯。", "canonical_ref": "27.56", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0057", "section_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i", "source_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 57, "text_original": "鄉者言曰：", "text_normalized": "鄉者言曰：", "canonical_ref": "27.57", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0058", "section_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i", "source_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 58, "text_original": "義人在上，天下必治，上帝、山川、鬼神必有干主，萬民被其大利。", "text_normalized": "義人在上，天下必治，上帝、山川、鬼神必有干主，萬民被其大利。", "canonical_ref": "27.58", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0059", "section_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i", "source_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 59, "text_original": "吾用此知之。", "text_normalized": "吾用此知之。", "canonical_ref": "27.59", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0060", "section_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i", "source_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 60, "text_original": "是故古之聖王，發憲出令，設以為賞罰以勸賢。", "text_normalized": "是故古之聖王，發憲出令，設以為賞罰以勸賢。", "canonical_ref": "27.60", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0061", "section_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i", "source_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 61, "text_original": "是以入則孝慈於親戚，出則弟長於鄉里，坐處有度，出入有節，男女有辨。", "text_normalized": "是以入則孝慈於親戚，出則弟長於鄉里，坐處有度，出入有節，男女有辨。", "canonical_ref": "27.61", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0062", "section_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i", "source_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 62, "text_original": "是故使治官府則不盜竊，守城則不崩叛，君有難則死，出亡則送。", "text_normalized": "是故使治官府則不盜竊，守城則不崩叛，君有難則死，出亡則送。", "canonical_ref": "27.62", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0063", "section_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i", "source_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 63, "text_original": "此上之所賞，而百姓之所譽也。", "text_normalized": "此上之所賞，而百姓之所譽也。", "canonical_ref": "27.63", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0064", "section_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i", "source_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 64, "text_original": "執有命者之言曰：", "text_normalized": "執有命者之言曰：", "canonical_ref": "27.64", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0065", "section_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i", "source_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 65, "text_original": "「上之所賞，命固且賞，非賢故賞也。", "text_normalized": "「上之所賞，命固且賞，非賢故賞也。", "canonical_ref": "27.65", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0066", "section_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i", "source_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 66, "text_original": "上之所罰，命固且罰，命固且罰，不暴故罰也。", "text_normalized": "上之所罰，命固且罰，命固且罰，不暴故罰也。", "canonical_ref": "27.66", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0067", "section_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i", "source_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 67, "text_original": "」是故入則不慈孝於親戚，出則不弟長於鄉里，坐處不度，出入無節，男女無辨。", "text_normalized": "」是故入則不慈孝於親戚，出則不弟長於鄉里，坐處不度，出入無節，男女無辨。", "canonical_ref": "27.67", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0068", "section_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i", "source_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 68, "text_original": "是故治官府則盜竊，守城則崩叛，君有難則不死，出亡則不送。", "text_normalized": "是故治官府則盜竊，守城則崩叛，君有難則不死，出亡則不送。", "canonical_ref": "27.68", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0069", "section_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i", "source_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 69, "text_original": "此上之所罰，百姓之所非毀也。", "text_normalized": "此上之所罰，百姓之所非毀也。", "canonical_ref": "27.69", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0070", "section_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i", "source_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 70, "text_original": "執有命者言曰：", "text_normalized": "執有命者言曰：", "canonical_ref": "27.70", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0071", "section_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i", "source_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 71, "text_original": "「上之所罰，命固且罰，不暴故罰也。", "text_normalized": "「上之所罰，命固且罰，不暴故罰也。", "canonical_ref": "27.71", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0072", "section_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i", "source_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 72, "text_original": "上之所賞命固且賞，非賢故賞也。", "text_normalized": "上之所賞命固且賞，非賢故賞也。", "canonical_ref": "27.72", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0073", "section_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i", "source_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 73, "text_original": "」以此為君則不義，為臣則不忠，為父則不慈，為子則不孝，為兄則不長，為弟則不弟。", "text_normalized": "」以此為君則不義，為臣則不忠，為父則不慈，為子則不孝，為兄則不長，為弟則不弟。", "canonical_ref": "27.73", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0074", "section_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i", "source_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 74, "text_original": "而強執此者，此特凶言之所自生，而暴人之道也。", "text_normalized": "而強執此者，此特凶言之所自生，而暴人之道也。", "canonical_ref": "27.74", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0075", "section_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i", "source_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 75, "text_original": "然則何以知命之為暴人之道？", "text_normalized": "然則何以知命之為暴人之道？", "canonical_ref": "27.75", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0076", "section_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i", "source_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 76, "text_original": "昔上世之窮民，貪於飲食，惰於從事，是以衣食之財不足，而饑寒凍餒之憂至。", "text_normalized": "昔上世之窮民，貪於飲食，惰於從事，是以衣食之財不足，而饑寒凍餒之憂至。", "canonical_ref": "27.76", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0077", "section_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i", "source_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 77, "text_original": "不知曰我罷不肖，從事不疾，必曰我命固且貧。", "text_normalized": "不知曰我罷不肖，從事不疾，必曰我命固且貧。", "canonical_ref": "27.77", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0078", "section_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i", "source_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 78, "text_original": "昔上世暴王，不忍其耳目之淫，心塗之辟，不順其親戚，遂以亡失國家，傾覆社稷。", "text_normalized": "昔上世暴王，不忍其耳目之淫，心塗之辟，不順其親戚，遂以亡失國家，傾覆社稷。", "canonical_ref": "27.78", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0079", "section_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i", "source_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 79, "text_original": "不知曰我罷不肖，為政不善，必曰吾命固失之。", "text_normalized": "不知曰我罷不肖，為政不善，必曰吾命固失之。", "canonical_ref": "27.79", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0080", "section_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i", "source_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 80, "text_original": "於《仲虺之告》曰：", "text_normalized": "於《仲虺之告》曰：", "canonical_ref": "27.80", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0081", "section_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i", "source_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 81, "text_original": "「我聞於夏人，矯天命，布命於下。", "text_normalized": "「我聞於夏人，矯天命，布命於下。", "canonical_ref": "27.81", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0082", "section_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i", "source_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 82, "text_original": "帝伐之惡，龔喪厥師。", "text_normalized": "帝伐之惡，龔喪厥師。", "canonical_ref": "27.82", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0083", "section_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i", "source_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 83, "text_original": "」此言湯之所以非桀之執有命也。", "text_normalized": "」此言湯之所以非桀之執有命也。", "canonical_ref": "27.83", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0084", "section_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i", "source_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 84, "text_original": "於《太誓》曰：", "text_normalized": "於《太誓》曰：", "canonical_ref": "27.84", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0085", "section_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i", "source_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 85, "text_original": "「紂夷處，不肯事上帝鬼神，禍厥先神禔不祀，乃曰：", "text_normalized": "「紂夷處，不肯事上帝鬼神，禍厥先神禔不祀，乃曰：", "canonical_ref": "27.85", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0086", "section_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i", "source_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 86, "text_original": "『吾民有命。", "text_normalized": "『吾民有命。", "canonical_ref": "27.86", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0087", "section_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i", "source_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 87, "text_original": "無廖排漏』。", "text_normalized": "無廖排漏』。", "canonical_ref": "27.87", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0088", "section_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i", "source_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 88, "text_original": "天亦縱棄之而弗葆。", "text_normalized": "天亦縱棄之而弗葆。", "canonical_ref": "27.88", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0089", "section_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i", "source_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 89, "text_original": "」此言武王所以非紂執有命也。", "text_normalized": "」此言武王所以非紂執有命也。", "canonical_ref": "27.89", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0090", "section_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i", "source_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 90, "text_original": "今用執有命者之言，則上不聽治，下不從事。", "text_normalized": "今用執有命者之言，則上不聽治，下不從事。", "canonical_ref": "27.90", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0091", "section_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i", "source_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 91, "text_original": "上不聽治，則刑政亂；", "text_normalized": "上不聽治，則刑政亂；", "canonical_ref": "27.91", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0092", "section_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i", "source_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 92, "text_original": "下不從事，則財用不足。", "text_normalized": "下不從事，則財用不足。", "canonical_ref": "27.92", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0093", "section_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i", "source_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 93, "text_original": "上無以供粢盛酒醴，祭祀上帝鬼神，下無以降綏天下賢可之士，外無以應待諸侯之賓客，內無以食饑衣寒，將養老弱。", "text_normalized": "上無以供粢盛酒醴，祭祀上帝鬼神，下無以降綏天下賢可之士，外無以應待諸侯之賓客，內無以食饑衣寒，將養老弱。", "canonical_ref": "27.93", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0094", "section_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i", "source_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 94, "text_original": "故命上不利於天，中不利於鬼，下不利於人。", "text_normalized": "故命上不利於天，中不利於鬼，下不利於人。", "canonical_ref": "27.94", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0095", "section_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i", "source_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 95, "text_original": "而強執此者，此特凶言之所自生，而暴人之道也！", "text_normalized": "而強執此者，此特凶言之所自生，而暴人之道也！", "canonical_ref": "27.95", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0096", "section_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i", "source_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 96, "text_original": "是故子墨子言曰：", "text_normalized": "是故子墨子言曰：", "canonical_ref": "27.96", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0097", "section_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i", "source_id": "mozi-027-anti-fatalism-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 97, "text_original": "今天下之士君子，忠實欲天下之富而惡其貧，欲天下之治而惡其亂，執有命者之言不可不非，此天下之大害也。", "text_normalized": "今天下之士君子，忠實欲天下之富而惡其貧，欲天下之治而惡其亂，執有命者之言不可不非，此天下之大害也。", "canonical_ref": "27.97", "notes": ""}
